content:
Set up and configure Data Cloud for Financial Services Cloud.

Financial Services Cloud is available in Lightning Experience. Available in: Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions.

To use Data Cloud for Financial Services Cloud:
 
Salesforce org: Financial Services Cloud Extension OR FSC Sales OR FSC Service

AND
 
Data Cloud org: Data Cloud Admin

To set up Data Cloud for Financial Services cloud, review and complete these steps:

Get Started.
Plan your Data Cloud Strategy.
Set Up a Data Cloud Admin User.
Turn On Data Cloud.
Manage Data Cloud Users.
Manage Access with Data Cloud Permission Sets.
Data Space Permission Sets.
Set Up the Salesforce CRM Connector.
Verify the Financial Services Cloud SSOT Version.
Connect Data Cloud to Your Salesforce Org.
Enable Object and Field Permissions for Financial Services Cloud Objects.
title: Setting Up Data Cloud for Financial Services Cloud
